    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and dependable performance. This unit has been meticulously curated to ensure lasting reliability and aesthetic refinement. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle at a strategic value point.",
      "price": 31500.0,
